Name: Pesto Pasta
Steps: Bold pasta in water for 5-7 min
Mixed pesto in to pasta to fully covered

Name: Chicken Parmesan
Steps: shallow fry the chicken till cooked
Bold pasta in water for 5-7 min
Add cooked pasta to plate and lay the chicken on top
Add a slice of mozzarella to the top of the chicken

Name: Margherita Pizza
Steps: Spread Sauce over the top of the dough
place slices of Mozzarella over the pizza
top with a few leafs of basil
